timeline.bodyText:
Instead of using null ptr, maybe we could get a NoOpTypeClassGenerator which will do nothing for generateAndWrite, and remove the outputName() to make one single API. Something like
String outputFileName = typeClassGenerator.generateAndWrite(outputDir, writer);

I don't feel strong about this change, ideally it should look better, but up to you.

